{"id":237046,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-成都访民陈茜应约到最高院接谈被送久敬/","date":"2012-07-03T04:46:20Z","modified":"2012-07-03T04:46:20Z","title":"维权网 | 成都访民陈茜应约到最高院接谈被送久敬庄关押","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div align=\"left\"> </div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>（维权网信息员李雅琴报道）据成都访民陈茜在电话中称：她应最高法院</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>的预约接淡，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日下午</span><span>约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>点钟在天安门公交车站被警方非法扣押到天安门分局，于当晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>点左右被送往久敬庄黑监狱关押，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">38</span><span>分被当地武侯区警察蔡彬（警号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">009413</span><span>）接出久敬庄押上了一辆黑保安的车，一同截访的人员还有金牛区人北街道办事处人北社区治保主任徐敏。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>   </span></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>据陈茜说：与她一同被截访送上黑保安车上的人员还有两个新津县的访民和一个彭县的访民，总共四个人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>   </span></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>因为是在七一期间上访，上访回当地后很多人被成都当局拘留。陈茜一行人现在还不好说，他们担心遭到成都当局的报复性拘留。希望社会关注他们的安全。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-653522396856177584?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击